      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把四个参与者排好：W1标注为\"Write v=42, t=1000\"，T1是\"RowTombstone t=2000\"，W2是\"Write v=new, t=3000\"，还有TTL Expiry。然后在W1上方加note说明value 42的可见性。",
